dct_description_sm: Revised 1942. Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. G.S.G.S. no. 4241. United States. Army Map Service. Alternate title: Fes: city plan. In upper left margin: Morocco 1:10,000. Relief shown bt 2.5 meter contour intervals and spot elevations. Lambert conical orthomorphic projection. N.W. Africa Zone grid. Copied from a French map dated 1933.
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1942.
